# 📝 Todo Planner App

A simple full-stack **Todo Application** built with:

- 🖥️ **Frontend:** React + TypeScript  
- ⚙️ **Backend:** Spring Boot 3.x (Java 23)  
- 🗄️ **Database:** PostgreSQL  
- 🎨 **Theme:** Dark, modern, minimalistic  

> [!NOTE]
> A simple project, yet powerful enough for full stack education.

## 🚀 Features (MVP)
- User Authentication (username/password)
- Create, Read, Update, Delete Todos
- Logout functionality
- Responsive, clean UI

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React 18
- TypeScript
- React Router
- Axios
- Tailwind CSS (or shadcn/ui)

### Backend
- Spring Boot 3.x
- Spring Security (JWT Auth)
- Spring Data JPA
- PostgreSQL

